{"tid":633716,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"全球首部 Android 系統衛星電話面世","createTime":"2018-04-18T14:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T14:15:45.000Z","uid":28366,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d13fffb09eb75ae6680c8b0c5a60fdac1d993a5d","tid":633716,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"不少政府項目和能源開發的工作人員，或者是非牟利團體或人道救援組織的成員都需要在人跡罕至，無法接收到網絡的地區工作。這個時候要跟外界保持聯繫，就非靠衛星電話不可。很難想像在智能手機推出多年，幾乎人人都手執一部的時候，衛星電話一直未智能化。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/18/221713_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F18%2F221713_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8c1282ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主力生產衛星通訊裝置的 Thuraya 早前發表全球首部 Android 系統的衛星電話，Thuraya X5 Touch 配備一塊 5.2 吋觸控屏幕，解像度為 1080p，屏幕以 Gorilla Glass 強化玻璃保護，手機機身有 IP67 防水防塵功能。除了作為衛星電話，Thuraya X5 Touch 擁有雙 SIM 卡插槽，可以支援 2G、3G 和 4G 網絡，用戶能夠隨時在一般電訊網絡和衛星服務更切換。<br />\n<br />\n手機配備了高容量電池，但未有透露實際容量，還支援藍牙、Wi-Fi 和 NFC，亦配備了前後相機鏡頭。為了配合衛星電話用戶的特殊需要，Thuraya X5 Touch 的機身有專門用作求救的 SOS 按鈕，亦有先進的 GPS 導航功能。手機使用 Android 7.0 系統，可以透過 Google Play 安裝軟件，可惜 Thuraya 未有透露發售日期和定價。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/04/18/thuraya-x5-touch-first-android-satellite-phone/mobile-phone/?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=fbnew-50&amp;utm_campaign=unwire.hk+auto+boost+post+50shares+1102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F04%2F18%2Fthuraya-x5-touch-first-android-satellite-phone%2Fmobile-phone%2F%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dfbnew-50%26utm_campaign%3Dunwire.hk%2Bauto%2Bboost%2Bpost%2B50shares%2B1102&d=o%2FPBgnZAqpsRyg6bO2uhdPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=495180f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/04/18/thuraya-x5-touch-first-android-satellite-phone/mobile-phone/?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=fbnew-50&amp;utm_campaign=unwire.hk+auto+boost+post+50shares+1102</a>"},{"pid":"49151bb8376294efffd9f897c2be4e21103320b0","tid":633716,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:29:54.000Z","msg":"好似幾正，救命機"},{"pid":"19530ffff9f6ff02e6ef5ff2dae086e81843c880","tid":633716,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3192e850d18c6bdf1cd2f504a3f9e4699bafb03f","tid":633716,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T14:15:45.000Z","msg":"香港唔會賣小眾機，完"}]}